#@#
<!-- HTML File : Div tag with id -->

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Div tag with id</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="a1">
        <h1>SWORDIGO 🔮</h1>
        <h2>Download this app from Google Playstore now!</h2>
        <h3>It's totally Free with no additional charges @Rs.0/-</h3>
        <h4>Create your own customized #Avatar</h4>
        <h5>Master of Chaos is ready to fight with you :)</h5>
        <h6>*click here to get more details*</h6>
        <p>Welcome to the world of magic and adventures.</p>
        <p>
            Step into the multiverse of Swordigo where every corner 
            hides danger and discovery. As a young trainee, you will 
            wield mighty swords, cast powerful spells and explore 
            dark dungeons filled with chamber of secrets. Guided by
            the spirit of your fallen master, your destiny is to
            reforge the legendary mageblade and challenge the forces
            of evil. Embark on the journey where the fate of the 
            realm lies in your hands.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


